      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこれは私からの気持ちです、受け取って下さい",
      "startTime": 2.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4448.072465299999,
          "startTime": 6.7814057986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　これ、俺がもらっていいのか？\n琴乃からのプレゼントなんて、なんだろうなぁ",
      "startTime": 10.4814057986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "チョコレートです\n{user}さんの口に合えばいいんですけど",
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　でも、か、勘違いしないで下さいね\nこれはあくまで、いつもお世話になってるお礼ですから",
      "startTime": 23.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、義理チョコでも、もらえるだけで嬉しいよ",
      "startTime": 26.6766667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁこの前は、芽衣が「本命だよ」なんて言って\n渡してくるから、あれはちょっと焦ったけど",
      "startTime": 34.4433334033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ほ、本命チョコを！？\n芽衣が、{user}さんに！？",
      "startTime": 40.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いやいや、誤解なんだ。本人はどうも\n『本命』の意味がよく分かってなかったみたいでな……",
      "startTime": 45.8536500295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ああ、そういうことですか\n芽衣ってば、なんでそんな変な覚え方しちゃったんだろ",
      "startTime": 55.8999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}